<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />Blessed be the Lord, who daily bears our burdens,</para>

<para style="q1">the God who is our salvation.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />Our God is a God who saves;</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh the Lord is the one who is able to rescue us from death.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />But God will strike through the heads of his enemies,</para>

<para style="q1">through the hairy scalps of those who walk in offenses against him.</para>
